@backonmyfeet empowers people to achieve economic independence through fitness and community. Operating in 16 cities across the United States, Back on My Feet has been breaking cycles of poverty and addiction since 2007. 

Join us in cheering on the nine Atlanta community members representing Back on My Feet this Sunday @nycmarathon. 🙌 Watch the full film to learn more about this revolutionary organization at the 🔗 in our bio.
